INSERT INTO games (engine_game_id, board_size, game_type, status, created_at, archived_at, gcs_path, archive_version)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, 'finished', $4, $5, $6, $7)
        ON CONFLICT (engine_game_id) DO UPDATE SET
            archived_at = $5,
            gcs_path = $6,
            archive_version = $7,
            updated_at = $5
